                <head>402. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d402fn1">Source: Carter Library, Plains File,
                        President’s Daily Diary, Box 10, 7/17–30/78. Secret. The meeting took place
                        in the White House Situation Room. <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1"
                            >Carter</persName> wrote “Zbig, J” in the upper right-hand corner of the
                        page.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            from="1980-01-04T09:25:00-05:00" to="1980-01-04T10:25:00-05:00">January
                            4, 1980, 9:25–10:25 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <list type="subject">
                    <head>SUBJECT</head>
                    <item>Pakistan—Funding Issues</item>
